<b>Alma:</b> "If I can bring him back, what are you hoping to say to him?"
<b>Jonah:</b> "..."
<b>Jonah:</b> "I'm sorry."
<b>Jonah:</b> "If you can bring him back, I want to tell him that I'm sorry I couldn't save him."
<b>Jonah:</b> "He always had my back when I needed him."
<b>Jonah:</b> "Always in the nick of <b>time</b>; I never doubted that I could count on him. But when he needed me most... I ran for my life. Like a coward."
<b>Narration:</b> Jonah's all choked up...

